        <h2 class="title"><a href="/shoot-nikon-please-help-review-my-article-choosing-lenses-nikon-cameras">Shoot Nikon? Please help review my article on choosing lenses for Nikon cameras</a></h2>    <span class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="/user/brad" title="View user profile." rel="nofollow">brad</a> on Sun, 2010-11-14 16:47.</span>
    <span class="taxonomy"><ul class="links inline"><li class="first taxonomy_term_1"><a href="/archives/cat_photography.html" rel="tag" title="" class="taxonomy_term_1">Photography</a></li>
<li class="last taxonomy_term_36"><a href="/taxonomy/term/36" rel="tag" title="For problems I&#039;ve been thinking about that need better ideas.  Your input is welcome." class="taxonomy_term_36">Solve this</a></li>
